                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 7370/33.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the <gloss type="to">Norwegian Chargé</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1910-07-02">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 2, 1910</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>This Government learns with deep regret of the death of Mr. Gude. Pray accept and
                    convey to your Government the expression of the sincerest sympathy.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Huntington Wilson.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
